      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an exemplary vehicle maintained to showroom standards. This unit exhibits no discernible wear, featuring a flawless exterior finish and a pristine interior cabin. Mechanically, it performs with the precision of a new vehicle, offering an uncompromising driving experience for the most discerning professional.",
      "price": 46500.0,
